---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms & Conditions | AryanForge"
  description="Terms and conditions governing the use of AryanForge's AI automation, web development, and digital product services.">

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-grotesk font-bold tracking-tight text-primary">
        Terms & <span class="gradient-gold">Conditions</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted mt-2">Last updated: June 15, 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 space-y-8 prose-body">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          By accessing or using the AryanForge website, services, or digital products ("Services"), you agree to be bound by these Terms & Conditions. If you do not agree, do not use our Services.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">2. Services Description</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          AryanForge provides AI automation solutions, premium web development, AI chatbot systems, SEO automation services, and digital products. All services are provided on a project-by-project or subscription basis as agreed in your service agreement or order confirmation.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">3. Client Responsibilities</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          You agree to: (a) provide accurate and complete information required for service delivery; (b) maintain confidentiality of any login credentials; (c) not use our Services for any unlawful purpose; (d) not reverse-engineer, copy, or redistribute our proprietary software, templates, or AI agents without written permission.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          All custom work delivered (code, designs, AI agents) becomes your intellectual property upon full payment. AryanForge retains the right to display completed work in our portfolio unless otherwise agreed. Our digital products, templates, and boilerplates are licensed, not sold — you may use them for commercial projects but may not resell or redistribute them as standalone products.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">5. Payments & Billing</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Project fees are due as per the agreed payment schedule. Subscription services are billed monthly and auto-renew unless cancelled 7 days before renewal. All payments are processed securely via Razorpay. Prices are in INR (Indian Rupees) unless otherwise specified; USD conversions are approximate.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">6. Refund Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Custom development projects: 50% refundable before development begins. Once development has started, no refund is available on work completed. Digital products (store): all sales final due to the digital nature of the goods. Subscription services: cancel anytime with no long-term contract; month-to-month billing only. We guarantee satisfaction on all custom projects — we work with you until deliverables meet the agreed specifications.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          AryanForge shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from the use or inability to use our Services. Our total liability is limited to the amount paid by you for the specific service giving rise to the claim. We do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free operation of AI systems, as AI models may produce unexpected outputs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">8. AI System Disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          AI systems built by AryanForge use large language models (LLMs) that may occasionally produce inaccurate or unexpected outputs. You acknowledge that: (a) AI outputs should be reviewed before acting upon them; (b) you are responsible for compliance with applicable laws in your use of AI; (c) AryanForge is not liable for decisions made based on AI-generated content.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">9. Confidentiality</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We treat all client information, business processes, and project data as confidential. We will not share, sell, or disclose your information to third parties except as necessary to deliver our Services or as required by law. NDAs available on request.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">10. Termination</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          Either party may terminate a service agreement with 30 days written notice. Upon termination, you pay for all work completed up to the termination date. Digital product access and delivered work remain yours.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">11. Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          These terms are governed by the laws of India. Any disputes shall be resolved through binding arbitration in accordance with the Arbitration and Conciliation Act, 1996.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-grotesk font-bold text-primary mb-3">12. Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes are effective immediately upon posting. Your continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-6 border-t border-default">
        <p class="text-sm text-secondary">
          Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:aryan@launchwitharyan.ai" class="text-gold hover:text-gold-dim">aryan@launchwitharyan.ai</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .prose-body h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  .prose-body p { line-height: 1.75; }
</style>
